<section id="Deleting_a_Policy_Profile" remap="TID_14767">
	<title>Deleting a Policy Profile</title>
	<para>
		Remove policy profiles that you no longer need. This does not remove the policies associated with the policy profile.
	</para>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Delete a Policy Profile</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to <menuchoice><guimenu>Control</guimenu><guisubmenu>Explorer</guisubmenu></menuchoice>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click on the <guimenu>Policy Profile</guimenu> accordion, then click the policy profile you want to remove.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1847.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> (<guilabel>Configuration</guilabel>), 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1861.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> (<guilabel>Remove this Policy Profile</guilabel>).
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click <guibutton>OK</guibutton> to confirm.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
</section>